1. DESCRIPTION

Warcraft II players should know this after running the program. It's an editor
for battlecraft (a god-game, like warcraft and populous). The game itself is
not released yet (more info later) but the editor will give a good impression
how it will/could look like.

I've already drawn a landscape and added some puds to try out. Thats right! you
can convert/view warcraft II levels (128*128 only) Also most map options (like
starting conditions and map description) are supported.



2. SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS

None.. except for the AMIGA of course :)



3. MAPS WANTED

The editor supports multiple map names which enables you to load and save
different landscapes! Because of this you can finally create your own maps. Why
not share these maps with rest of the world by sending them to me so i can put
them on my page? I might even decide to use them in the game if they're good
enough! :)



