5. INSTRUCTIONS

<KEYS>
-----------
F1          - create a snapshot (../battlecraft/snapshot.iff)
F10         - menu (load, save, clear map and quit)

arrowkeys   - scroll on map (or use the mini-map)


<BUTTONS>
-----------
!-button    - to change/view names of peasants and goldamount in mines!
X-button    - to delete peasants and buildings
menu-button - to show the menu (same as F10)


<SHELL>
-----------
The editor now has versionsupport. Open a shell and type: version Battlecraft-ED



